Pickard, Appellant, v. Carr et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. April 13, 1892.) Action by Nancy E. Pickard against James Carr and another.

Argued before Dwight, P. J., and Macomber and Lewis, JJ.

$0 opinion. Judgment appealed from affirmed. See 17 N. Y. Supp,. 605, ■mem..
